dcterms:description: The Adult data set originates from the 1994 Census database, consisting of 14 attributes and 48,842 instances. The classification consists of deciding whether an individual has an income greater than 50,000 USD/year.
dcterms:title: Adult

dcterms:description: The Give Me Some Credit (GMC) data set from a 2011 Kaggle Competition is a credit scoring data set, consisting of 150,000 observations and 11 features. The classification task consists of deciding whether an instance will experience financial distress within the next two years.
dcterms:title: Give Me Some Credit (GMC)
